room_title: Escape room "The Crypt" by Streaper's Escape Adventures in Wabash
room_description:
Meet Elanore Greenworth... a widow of many men. Marry them, and bury them always said. Some husbands just can't hold their arsenic.
She now has met her own demise and has been buried with her greatest love; her money. A crypt with a trap... you're locked in! With only 60 minutes left of oxygen, can you find the money and escape in time to set things right for the late Mr. Greenworth?!
